</div><div class="t m350 x74 h1b y198 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Mary, that was a beautiful experience you shared. I don&apos;t </div><div class="t m69 x9 h1b yb9f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">see how you can work in that soup kitchen in the inner-city area and </div><div class="t m110 x15 h1b y19b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">love those people the way you do. But I admire you and can see how </div><div class="t m8e x9 h1b y19c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord works through you.&quot; </div><div class="t m316 x18 h23 y19d ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pete: </div><div class="t m387 x68 h1b yba0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;John, when you shared how God met your needs through that </div><div class="t m48a x9 h1b y19f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">passage in 2 Corinthians, I can&apos;t tell you how encouraging it was to </div><div class="t m25c x9 h1b y65d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">me. I&apos;m experiencing a problem like that, and God used you to help me </div><div class="t m4b0 x15 h1b y1a1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">face it.&quot; </div><div class="t m30f x38 h23 y1a2 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Martha: </div><div class="t m3da x10 h1b y65e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I believe God wants the kind of warm, vital fellowship </div><div class="t m324 x9 h1b y9e6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we have to spread through our whole church. I have a growing convic-</div><div class="t m1df x9 h1b y65f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion that God is going to do some spectacular things in our church. I </div><div class="t m83 x9 h1b yc4e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have this deep conviction that a year from now this church is really </div><div class="t m192 x9 h1b y1a5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">going to take off. I can just see how John 17 will be a reality in our </div><div class="t m21e x9 h1b y9bc ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church.&quot; </div><div class="t m23d x38 h23 y9bd ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jerry: </div><div class="t m6c4 x4d h1b y9bd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I made another friend at work t